# Title Format Rules
- **Category Prefix**: Use appropriate category in brackets (예: [Movie], [TV Series], [Algorithm], [Vocabulary])
- **Main Title**: Human-readable, SEO-optimized title
- **Length**: Keep total title under 70 characters

# Date Management Best Practices
- **Current Date**: Always use today's date obtained via command line
- **Date Updates**: Update `lastmod` when content is significantly revised

# 기타 메타데이터
- 제목·날짜 외 메타데이터(tags 50개 이상, description 150자, title 길이 등)는 **rules-that-must-be-followed**를 참조한다.
